=== Noun ===
'''fire truck'''

# A [[ladder]] truck, a [[vehicle]] used by [[firefighter]]s to gain access to the upper stories of a building. Typically, a fire truck has a [[hydraulic]] system which operates a large, heavy-duty ladder mounted on top of the truck body, space for portable ladders to be stored and compartments for holding other tools that may be needed. 
# Any fire [[apparatus]], including fire trucks, fire engines and rescue squads.

